{"tid":1717391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得依家又變返唔「be water」？","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:15:43.000Z","uid":4646,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de5265a9bd23a854aef20ad9b4c3c2f422f47b43","tid":1717391,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"事前講定：「be water」解流水唔係解散水，我唔會叫邊個地方嘅人留或走，要叫就自己落去叫<br />\n<br />\n依家中大班狗減少衝擊中大但仲係吐露港standby，而禁制令唔批，咁會做成中大隨時被攻，令到中大要一班人入面守<br />\n<br />\n城大 港大 浸大都有一班人守緊，而警方係上午之後冇大動作進攻但都standby, 令又有幾班人係依三大守<br />\n<br />\n而今日出面上水、中環、葵涌邨、青衣等地開戰<br />\n<br />\n圍魏救趙係拉開警力，但依家警察都好似將一班抗爭者鎖係四大，假如四大依家走，但一旦走得唔好就落單拉幾件。相反，繼續唔走就警察可以確定有一班抗爭者係四大入面，咁出面流水緊嘅人就少好多<br />\n<br />\n重複一次唔係散水亦都唔係叫人死守，只係想討論依家戰況，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人想叫人走或唔好走，麻煩自己落場講</span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9bb0df1dd67dd3a93f62b74696c3b947da834a","tid":1717391,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b3363a4b9e543c2a8aca91ad1985d4febb5fdc","tid":1717391,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:08:22.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n本身係保中大先咁做<br />\n唔應該變長久"},{"pid":"562adf06ae9dc9ea45ff7c0c18c5ba2fe09f868f","tid":1717391,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfd6ae4dcd35378cc7b326fd030af3a77357f13","tid":1717391,"uid":10466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:19:45.000Z","msg":"Be 你老母咩，比人打到門口，重要be water"},{"pid":"508743efbb50ea63584acf7be54f7eb45c77b9a6","tid":1717391,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bfd6ae4dcd35378cc7b326fd030af3a77357f13","tid":1717391,"uid":10466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:19:45.000